originalText.text:
If you are a service provider, DO NOT work for this company. They DO NOT PAY invoices. My company provided snow plowing services this winter, on a fixed rate contract that should be paid in equal monthly  installments however, we have not seen a penny. Invoices and services date back over 4 months. We are now being told by our contact at Park My Fleet that upper management has decided they just don't want to pay yet and he doesn't know when they will want too.

Stay away from this company. They take advantage of service providers and I'm sure customers too.
